			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>Job Description:</strong></p>
<p>
Are you the type of person that strives to be better than the next? Do you have a fire inside that burns and is not settled until you achieve ultimate singularity with the universe? . . . or do you just like to work hard and play foosball!?!&nbsp; If you are nodding yes to any of this, PayJunction needs you as the next part-time Sales Recruiter to help staff our outside sales force.</p>
<p>
This job is not for the faint of heart. We like to live by the &quot;work hard, play hard&quot; mentality, but if you can&#39;t handle the first half of that phrase, then this isn&#39;t the place for you. We believe in setting and attaining personal goals, coming into work with a positive attitude, and enjoying a casual office environment with our peers. If you have the work ethic to be a superstar recruiter, the friendly disposition of a golden retriever, and the humility it takes to lose at beer pong to your boss, then we want to meet you!</p>
<p>
PayJunction is a financial software company founded in 2000 by UCSB Computer Science graduates. We are constantly blazing new trails in our industry, and are looking for the best and brightest new additions to help continue our growth. The Sales Recruiter position is perfect for students. . .we work around your school schedule and offer competitive pay for those seeking to gain experience in a unique corporate environment where there is always room for growth!!</p>
<p>
Perfect for students or others looking for a part-time position. We do provide complete training for the position so no experience is required.</p>
<p>
<strong>Environment:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
10,000 square foot corporate HQ in downtown Santa Barbara, California</li>
<li>
Onsite movie theatre with 40+ bean bags</li>
<li>
Onsite bar and kegerator with chalkboard walls, flat screen tv, direct tv, Pay Per View UFC Matches</li>
<li>
Boardroom/Game rooms with xbox, direct tv, apple tv</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Company Ethos:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
We value long term relationships over short term profit.</li>
<li>
We are building something that will last longer than us.</li>
<li>
We are passionate about our work and inspired by the team we have created.</li>
<li>
We create products that improve the lives of our customers.</li>
<li>
We build green technology that costs less than our prospective clients pay now.</li>
<li>
We are constantly innovating.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>About PayJunction:</strong></p>
<p>
PayJunction is the leading developer of paperless payment software, enabling businesses to process secure transactions in real-time from anywhere in the world. We are dedicated to building innovative products that make it easier for businesses to process payments in their office, through their website, and on the go.</p>
<p>
PayJunction has developed the first environmentally friendly product in the industry that&nbsp; allows businesses to process credit cards and checks using any computer, tablet, or cell phone.&nbsp; Our innovative products allow merchants to capture electronic signatures at the point of sale, and for the first time, remotely via email. PayJunction will eliminate the need to file away paper receipts, ultimately increasing productivity and reducing cost for small and medium sized businesses but more importantly reducing the carbon footprint of an entire industry.</p>
