<p>
<strong>Company Overview</strong></p>
<p>
PayJunction is the leading developer of paperless payment software, enabling businesses to process secure transactions in real-time from anywhere in the world. We are dedicated to building innovative products that make it easier for businesses to process payments in their office, through their website, and on the go.</p>
<p>
PayJunction has developed the first environmentally friendly product in the industry that&nbsp; allows businesses to process credit cards and checks using any computer, tablet, or cell phone. &nbsp;Our innovative products allow merchants to capture electronic signatures at the point of sale, and for the first time, remotely via email. PayJunction will eliminate the need to file away paper receipts, ultimately increasing productivity and reducing cost for small and medium sized businesses but more importantly reducing the carbon footprint of an entire industry.</p>
<p>
At PayJunction&nbsp; we value long-term relationships over short-term profits; this along with our commitment to&nbsp; advancing technology have been the foundation of our success. Founded in 2000 in Santa Barbara CA,&nbsp; PayJunction currently processes over 2 billion dollars a year for tens of thousands of businesses nationwide. Our industry-leading software&nbsp; has been propelling our growth by over 300% for each of the past 7 years.</p>
<p>
<strong>Job Description</strong></p>
<p>
PayJunction is leading the way for paperless processing and we are seeking Sales Representatives that will seize the opportunity to help us change the industry. As a well established company we offer the sales support and resources necessary to help update the millions of businesses still processing with outdated technology.</p>
<p>
We provide our sales reps with:</p>
<ul>
<li>
A dedicated sales director to help you navigate the industry and manage your accounts&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li>
Marketing material both physical and digital</li>
<li>
An online sales pipeline to easily manage clients and prospects</li>
<li>
A team of analysts for generating ROI&#39;s and rate analysis</li>
<li>
We handle customer and technical support in-house, so no account management on your end</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>
<p>
We are seeking independent and motivated individuals to join our sales team of over 350 active reps across the country. Our sales reps market our products and business solutions to merchants in their surrounding areas with the support and guidance of their sales director. If you are a creative individual with an entrepreneurial mind set, then PayJunction will inevitably provide the building blocks to your success.</p>
<p>
Our agents&nbsp; are responsible for:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Assistance in sales and marketing of our product to the businesses in their surrounding areas</li>
<li>
Identifying key target markets and qualified businesses&nbsp;for our free equipment program</li>
<li>
Working directly with corporate sales directors to build long-term lasting relationships with clients</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Benefits</strong><br />
<br />
PayJunction has given itself a huge leg up over its competition by innovating industry changing technologies never before offered on the market. This gives our sales team a unique advantage of being the first in the world to market a technology like this to small and medium sized business. Ultimately our reps enjoy the security and experience of working alongside an established company with proven success along with the flexibility and independence of managing a schedule that fits whatever lifestyle they desire.</p>
<ul>
<li>
Earn 65% of first year&#39;s profit on the account</li>
<li>
Full or part-time (1099)</li>
<li>
No quotas or territory restrictions</li>
<li>
Average starting income $60k (based on 5 to 10 accounts a month)</li>
</ul>
